summary: Book Review: Super Nutrition by Terry McIlroy
title: Book Review: Super Nutrition by Terry McIlroy
body:
Book Review: Super Nutrition by Terry McIlroy @fayerogersuk, @authoright

Title: Super Nutrition
Author: Terry McIlory
Release Date: 2nd May 2019
Genre: Non-Ficton
Page Count: 216
Publisher: Clink Street Publishing

We have all uttered these phrases at one time or another:

“Your health is your wealth.”

“You are what you eat.”

Deep down, we all know, that what we choose to eat and drink has a massive impact on our health.

Confused about your nutritional needs? Not…

caption:
As the famous biologist Charles Darwin said, “It is not the strongest of the species that survives, nor the most intelligent, but the one most responsive to change.”

In Darwinian terms, the outside environment is the catalyst for change, but the extraordinary thing about being human, is that we don’t have to wait for our ass to catch on fire because it gets hot out there, we can start changing things in here regardless of what is happening out there.
At tomorrow evenings workshop we will be focused on making those needed changes in your lifestyle to increase your level of happiness, success and well being.

tags: love when all your health problems hit you in one day
summary:
Hi guys 
Welcome back to my channel! 
Today I randomly got hip pain!!!
YAY
And it hasn’t gone away! I can barely walk on my...
body:
Hi guys

Welcome back to my channel!

Today I randomly got hip pain!!!

YAY

And it hasn’t gone away! I can barely walk on my right leg because the muscle feels so tight and the movement is that restricted!!

Omg can I have this girls life??

Not only this, but I have a headache and my eyes hurt!!

Woohoo!!

And I’ve had back pain for a good month now!!!

Omg thats gr8. So great infact, that it could be gr10.

And I’ve had a locked jaw for like a year now!

Omg so lucky I #lovemylife

And apparently I have scoliosis!!

Could this day get any better?????

My back is also itchy!

To be fair I don’t actually care about that!!

Got a mark back to day and it almost sucked but then I remembered it was only worth 5%

Love a failing queen (jk I didn’t fail)!!

I actually look like crap. I never understood raccoon eyes but I have raccoon eyes, and I haven’t even touched eyeliner to make it happen.

Love a beauty qween!!

My period is late but I don’t even do the sex

We love thinking we’re pregnant when we’re actually just sad and ugly virgins

Anyway thanks for watching my video!! If you are in pain, make sure to smash that like button, and why not hit that subscribe button while you’re at it. Don’t forget to ding that notification bell to know exactly when I’ve uploaded a new video and leave a comment down below if you can relate to any of my issues, and if you can’t, you might as well just let me know what your issues are anyway!!

Byeeee <3

summary:
La fatalité n'arrive qu'à ceux qui y croient
290419
These last few days I was not very happy to live and I'm still not... That...
body:
La fatalité n'arrive qu'à ceux qui y croient

290419

These last few days I was not very happy to live and I’m still not… That said, I think that even when bad events happen to us, as long as we do not give up, there is always a way to get out of them. Fatality is only the reality of liabilities. Be an actor of your own life and not just a spectator. Fix things like you were helping your best friend and you will find a way to succeed in overcoming your problems and creating the life you really want.

Don’t be afraid about what you can or can not do… Think of what you might miss if you don’t try.

Kinds words to you, all my love.
